(1, 'session', 'Women Career Opportunities in Data Science', 'women-career-opportunities-in-data-science', NULL, NULL, '2024-05-11', '7:30 - 8:30 PM', 'Online', 'Mumbai', '<div style=\"\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\" style=\"\"><font style=\"\">From Gap to Growth:&nbsp;</font></font></b><font face=\"Verdana\" style=\"\"><b>Women Career Opportunities in Data Science</b></font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Hey there! Are you ready to jumpstart your career in&nbsp;<b>Data Science</b>&nbsp;after taking a break? Weâ€™ve got the perfect opportunity for you!</font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\" style=\"\">Join us for a <b>FREE online session</b> designed for <b>women </b>looking to re-enter the workforce!&nbsp;</font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><br></font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><b>Date &amp; Time</b>: Saturday, 11th May 2024 - 7.30 PM - 8.30 PM</font></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-style: normal; font-variant-